title: Happy Tartans Apron (4 Colors)
description:
Welcome to Cafe Sumire a place full of roses, tea and music.

This listing is for the purchase of one Happy Tartans Apron. ♪✮ Happy Tartans ♪✮ is a collection inspired by japan kawaii nostalgia: lolita early days and the feminine urge for being Marie Antoinette while living in a modern small town.

Details

✮ Apron is made by tartan fabric we have completely produced in Barcelona. This tartan is exclusive by Violet Fane and Sumire, as we have personally dyied the treads to be the exact bright 80s colors we wanted for the collection.

✮ Cotton Fabric.

✮ It can be used with the bodice part attached to the skirt or it can be detached to use just the skirt part.

✮ It has multiple buttonholes on the straps to adjust different sizes.

✮ It has an embroidery Sumire logo.

Ready to ship.

So our recommendation to pick the size is that:

Pick Size 1 (XS-XL) if your Bust is 75-95cm and waist is 65-80cm

Pick Size 2 (XL-3XL) if your Bust is 95-135cm and waist is 80-110cm



Made by Violet Fane in Spain. Ships from our Independence location.

title: Instant Shipping! Jester Apron
description:
Made of soft velvet.

Comes with one removable 9in waist bow.

Contains aluminum wire for bending and shaping the tails.

 

For Size 1, the main waistband of the apron measures at 28 inches with the waist ties measuring 36 inches each, for a 100 inch total length. Best recommended for waists under 40 inches. Mannequin model is set at 28 inch waist.

For Size 2, the main waistband of the apron measures 43 inches with the waist ties  measuring 36 inches each, for a 115 inch total length. Best recommended for waists above 40 inches. Mannequin model is set at 40 inch waist.

title: Velveteen Rabbit Pinafore
description:
This soft and comfy pinafore is themed after the classic story The Velveteen Rabbit. Made from cotton velveteen, it features custom embroidered artwork and adorable bunny lace! The front pocket includes a quote from the story about becoming Real.

This pinafore has two pockets at the side seams and one decorative front pocket. The straps are adjustable with buttons, and it opens at the sides with buttons for easy dressing. 

The brown/mauve colorway is photographed over petticoat for a more dramatic shape. The other two colorways are pictured without the petticoat. Wear it with or without a petticoat for your desired silhouette.

Brand: Atelier Heidi
Materials: 100% cotton. Made in China.
Care: machine wash cold, tumble dry low or hang to dry

 

Size Chart

 Size Bust Waist
XS 31"-34" 26"-30"
S 34"-36" 30"-34"
M 36"-38" 34"-36"
L 38"-42" 36"-42"

3X 48"-54" 48"-54"
4X 52"-56" 52"-58"

These measurements are recommended body measurements. Choose the size closest to your actual measurements. The actual garment is slightly larger to account for wearing ease. All measurements in inches.

This item is made by Atelier Heidi in the USA. It ships from our US warehouse.
